abstract: Iranian news media reports at least 112 people have died from swine flu outbreak.
lead_paragraph: Deaths from a swine flu outbreak in Iran have more than tripled in the past three weeks to at least 112.

headline.main: Iran: Deaths From Swine Flu Rise
